RESEARCH USE ONLY

This software is intended for research purposes only and has not been validated
for clinical use. The models and methods provided are experimental and should
not be used for medical diagnosis, treatment decisions, or patient care without
appropriate clinical validation and regulatory approval.

Users must comply with all applicable laws and regulations regarding the use of
medical data and ensure appropriate ethical oversight for research involving
human subjects data.
